oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Richard D. Quillen interview
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Quillen, Richard D.; Caudill, Ed
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Quillen, Richard D.; Vietnam War, 1961-1975
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Richard Quillen served as a First Lieutenant in the U.S. Army during the Vietnam War from August 1969 to August 1970. The interview was conducted by Ed Caudill on June 11, 2019 at the Blount County Public Library.
